{"tid":1578442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵出軌原因，係波口故障，絕非示威者做成","createTime":"2019-09-18T06:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T15:52:08.000Z","uid":70493,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a75f16a0279ebc10d0c2e4d0f092d745b12e5679","tid":1578442,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.singtao.ca/3769704/2019-09-17/news-%E3%80%908.5%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E6%B6%89%E6%AF%80%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%87%88%E5%AE%98%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%9B%E8%AA%8D%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E5%9C%A8%E6%A1%88+%E5%85%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85/?variant=zh-hk&amp;desktopweb=1&amp;referid=3770989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2F3769704%2F2019-09-17%2Fnews-%25E3%2580%25908.5%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B6%2589%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%25A3%259E%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25A1%2588%2B%25E5%2585%25A9%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25BE%2585%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk%26desktopweb%3D1%26referid%3D3770989&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=2df6e406\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtao.ca/3769704/2019-09-17/news-%E3%80%908.5%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E3%80%91%E6%B6%89%E6%AF%80%E5%A3%9E%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E7%87%88%E5%AE%98%E5%B0%87%E6%8B%9B%E8%AA%8D%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E5%9C%A8%E6%A1%88+%E5%85%A9%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%8D%E7%95%B6%E5%B0%8D%E5%BE%85/?variant=zh-hk&amp;desktopweb=1&amp;referid=3770989</a><br />\n<br />\n【港鐵出軌】田北辰指或因「波口」配件鬆脫 相信有外物機會不大<br />\n2019年09月17日 07:19<br />\n<br />\n東鐵綫紅磡站的載客列車，早上約8時半出軌，導致8人受傷，港鐵人員仍然進行搶修。曾經擔任九鐵主席的實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰推斷，事故可能是由於俗稱「鴨脷」的尖軌鬆脫有關。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰指，列車低速入站時，信號系統會向路軌波口發出指示，移動「鴨脷」，並將「鴨脷」鎖死，令列車轉到正確的路軌繼續行駛，他懷疑事發時，列車部份車卡途經波口位後，本應被鎖死「鴨脷」在震盪下鬆脫，導致隨後的車卡脫軌，衝力扯開第四車卡，亦令路軌斷裂，海外亦曾發生類似事故。他認為，波口的設備理應每晚都有檢查，防止出問題。如果他推斷正確，是難以接受。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰又認為，有人向路軌投擲物品導致出軌的機會不大，否則列車理應第一卡就出軌；路軌斷開導致意外的機會不大，否則出軌列車會擺向同一方向，與目前情況不同。"},{"pid":"0b640cdbccf99e2734aa94ef6a038f3893e3a974","tid":1578442,"uid":268429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"唔講都知- -"},{"pid":"862be04d9fa4969f631330dc53471651bafb1586","tid":1578442,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:39:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c43594f1f57310e36c81ac01941859bb87ceae86","tid":1578442,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"e1d396f74773a959e8671f9747ba9db6e2ac9139","tid":1578442,"uid":237425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"田二少都講人話<br />\n而唔係咩9都入哂示威者數<br />\n<br />\n其實只要港資商家暗中OR隻眼開咁支援示威者<br />\n香港社會反支共力量其實有得打"},{"pid":"1223f42c4450c50bbfca93539b9c3477061b4f39","tid":1578442,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:43:28.000Z","msg":"唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d術語"},{"pid":"49f532cee78525645f1d2b79dab2131a598f5492","tid":1578442,"uid":306925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"借貴寶地<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1577137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n1）警察<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">衰野太多，好難一張文宣講晒</span></span></strong><br />\n2）我地前線手足都開始<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反擊得勁D，反擊畫面</span></span></strong>又會被現在好落力打國際戰的<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府拎黎大造文章，條片正好俾外國能更好地體諒我地</span></span></strong><br />\n3）更好利用一些<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">震撼畫面或者橋段，收籠外國人心</span></strong></span><br />\n4）微電影，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇故仔，好多人都會幾OK，有助spread</span></span></strong>我地情況出去<br />\n5）以後我地本地同外國<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣都塞條片的link入去</span></strong></span>，又或者YouTube channel<br />\n<br />\n但廢J我完全不識點樣整呢D片出來，卡通又好真人又好，都唔識，眾籌也沒experience。所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想集結神力，有邊位兄弟覺得有得諗，就幫手spread出去同用力push，小弟廢J P牌仔自push都做唔到</span></span></strong>，sosaad。"},{"pid":"eb61b1ac904f2580768dc629ce39540739d8318f","tid":1578442,"uid":293605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"載客期間出軌咁大鑊，政府好似冇出嚟正式譴責過港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4938167d8b031bf01934abe1f16cf1ba8fc6a6a7","tid":1578442,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb61b1ac904f2580768dc629ce39540739d8318f","tid":1578442,"uid":293605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:44:12.000Z","msg":"載客期間出軌咁大鑊，政府好似冇出嚟正式譴責過港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"御用黨鐵專車 自己友點會譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0eab91ae17a698485265233bc43ca4ee04836af","tid":1578442,"uid":302944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:49:49.000Z","msg":"我問題? 點解條link 同你篇文唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf48b245cb6a6d8e84c7c6e66a5074b34657c26","tid":1578442,"uid":282272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黨鐵水平, 出軌唔奇</span><br />\n真係得人驚<br />\n轉左做黨鐵之後就即刻整單咁嘅野"}]}